title: Episode 130: V-Card Revoked (ft Saige)
itunes:title: Episode 130: V-Card Revoked (ft Saige)
description:
On this weeks episode, the ladies of Lip Service give you their FIRST EVER interview update! Saige, who was previously on Lip Service back in August of 2016, with Slim Thug, revealed she was a 23 year old virgin. At the start of the episode, we will be flashing back to remind everyone about Saige's experiences as a virgin. After the flashback, the ladies sit with Saige to discuss life after sex, including tips and tricks moving forward.
